  "body" : "<blockquote>\n  <p><strong>Possible Duplicates:</strong><br>\n  <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/1957836/which-way-is-better-null-object-or-object-null\">which way is better &ldquo;null != object&rdquo; or &ldquo; object != null&rdquo;?</a><br>\n  <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/271561/why-does-one-often-see-null-variable-instead-of-variable-null-in-c\">Why does one often see &ldquo;null != variable&rdquo; instead of &ldquo;variable != null&rdquo; in C#?</a><br>\n  <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/2398588/null-or-null-best-performance\">&lsquo; &hellip; != null&rsquo;  or  &lsquo;null != &hellip;&rsquo; best performance?</a>  </p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n\n<p>Please guide me.\nwhat is the difference between null != object and object!=null<br>\nsame for \"\".equal(\"something\") and \"something\".equals(\"\")</p>\n\n<p>which one is good for processing.</p>\n"
